{"tid":278624,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[又爆多單] 撮合中港情緣 黃洋達認開交友公司","createTime":"2017-06-10T15:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T16:09:30.000Z","uid":105451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d9e791478a974e106ced3a59290118a8cd170451","tid":278624,"uid":105451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:18:40.000Z","msg":"熱血公民不時攻擊大陸人嚟香港搶資源，但有曾經支持熱普城嘅「苦主」同記者講，熱血首領黃洋達曾經開過一間speed dating公司「美滿人生」，撮合中港情侶。 <br />\n<br />\n公司註冊處資料顯示，「美滿人生」○七年七月成立，黃洋達係股東兼董事，一○年十一月已解散，但○九年公司負責人接受《蘋果》訪問時，講明中港婚姻大跌三分一，會定期舉辦中港交友派對。交友就冇乜所謂，但如果根據熱普城嘅講法，容乜易變咗大陸人嚟搶香港嘅筍盤？ <br />\n<br />\n究竟黃洋達係咪為咗做生意而不顧香港毒男宅女嘅福祉，引「蝗」入室？佢向本刊「澄清」呢間唔係經營中港婚姻嘅公司，只係做約會服務，但冇透露點解要結業，仲話之前佢喺網台節目都講過約會服務，唔係咩新嘢嚟喎。 <br />\n<br />\n神通廣大嘅高登仔引述節目內容，話黃大罵無綫節目《盛女愛作戰》嘅人生導師Winnie自己嘅人生都有問題，有乜資格檢討人哋嘅人生，仲話節目係植入式廣告。唔知開公司做中港約會但唔包生仔嘅黃洋達，又做唔做到其他人嘅人生導師？  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20160831/2_423159_0/%E6%92%AE%E5%90%88%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E6%83%85%E7%B7%A3-%E9%BB%83%E6%B4%8B%E9%81%94%E8%AA%8D%E9%96%8B%E4%BA%A4%E5%8F%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20160831%2F2_423159_0%2F%25E6%2592%25AE%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%25B7%25A3-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E6%25B4%258B%25E9%2581%2594%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%2596%258B%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8&d=wBcafSBMJWD7cDcEYs37IJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=5fe477d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20160831%2F2_423159_0%2F%25E6%2592%25AE%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2583%2585%25E7%25B7%25A3-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E6%25B4%258B%25E9%2581%2594%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%2596%258B%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8&h=3fc581f2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20160831/2_423159_0/%E6%92%AE%E5%90%88%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E6%83%85%E7%B7%A3-%E9%BB%83%E6%B4%8B%E9%81%94%E8%AA%8D%E9%96%8B%E4%BA%A4%E5%8F%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8</a>"},{"pid":"89262ad5a249bff6761b5798b9e309d9dd217e8b","tid":278624,"uid":105451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3708e556241184816cf893c03f2a02b91c758d18","tid":278624,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}